##Â Search Rats [GET /rats/{?platform,drilled.rescue}]

Search records of rats by matching fields

Scope: public

+ Parameters
  + id: `56a8c2bc9b884b56e9cfe8ba` (string, optional) - Return records where the ID matches
  + archive: `true` (boolean, optional) - Return records of rats that are archived
  + CMDRname: `Trezy` (string, optional) - Return records where the in-game username of this rat matches
  + createdAt: `2015-07-15T22%3A00%3A00.000Z` (string, optional) - Return records where the created date of the rat matches
  + drilled.dispatch: `true` (boolean, optional) - Return records of rats that are drilled for dispatching
  + drilled.rescue: `true` (boolean, optional) - Return records of rats that are drilled for rescuing
  + gamertag: `Trezy` (string, optional) - Return records of rats with a matching gamertag
  + lastModified: `2016-01-26T20%3A22%3A47.643Z` (string, optional) - Return records where the last modified date matches
  + joined: `2015-07-15T22%3A00%3A00.000Z` (string, optional) - Return records where the join date of the rat matches
  + nickname: `Trezy` (string, optional) - Return records where the IRC nickname of the rat matches
  + platform: `pc` (string, optional) - Return records where the platform of the rat matches

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
      + links (Link) - Links
      + meta (Meta) - Statistics on the current result
      + data (array[Rat]) - A list of rats
